{
  "info": {
    "name": "GoMobility — KYC v2",
    "_postman_id": "kyc-v2-collection",
    "description": "KYC v2 — OCR-first, admin-approved.\n\nFlow:\n1. Auth — Driver: run 'Signin' → copy OTP from console/SMS → run 'Verify Signin' → token auto-saved to {{driverToken}}\n2. Auth — Admin: same flow with admin phone 9999999999\n3. Driver uploads docs → all go to manual_review → admin reviews per-driver → approves/rejects\n\nLogin response includes kyc.nextScreen:\n  HOME               → KYC verified, show home\n  KYC_INTRO          → First time, show onboarding\n  KYC_UPLOAD         → In progress, show upload screen\n  KYC_UNDER_REVIEW   → All docs submitted, waiting\n  KYC_RETRY          → Some docs rejected, show retry\n  ACCOUNT_SUSPENDED  → Driver suspended",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl",      "value": "http://localhost:5000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "driverToken",  "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "adminToken",   "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "driverOtp",    "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "adminOtp",     "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "docId",        "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "driverUserId", "value": "",                      "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth — Driver Login",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Signin (send OTP)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"9876543210\",\n  \"role\": \"driver\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/signin",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "signin"]
            },
            "description": "Sends OTP to driver phone. Check server console (SMS_PROVIDER=console) for the OTP."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Verify Signin (get token + KYC status)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.success && json.data) {",
                  "  var d = json.data;",
                  "  if (d.tokens) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('driverToken', d.tokens.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('driverUserId', d.user.id);",
                  "  }",
                  "  if (d.kyc) {",
                  "    console.log('KYC status:', d.kyc.overallStatus, '| Next screen:', d.kyc.nextScreen);",
                  "  }",
                  "  console.log('Driver token saved. userId:', d.user ? d.user.id : 'N/A');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"9876543210\",\n  \"otp\": \"{{driverOtp}}\",\n  \"role\": \"driver\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/verify-signin",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "verify-signin"]
            },
            "description": "Response includes kyc object for drivers:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"tokens\": { \"accessToken\": \"...\", \"refreshToken\": \"...\" },\n  \"user\": { \"id\": \"...\", \"fullName\": \"...\", \"role\": \"driver\" },\n  \"kyc\": {\n    \"overallStatus\": \"not_started\",\n    \"submittedDocs\": 0,\n    \"verifiedDocs\": 0,\n    \"canGoOnline\": false,\n    \"verifiedAt\": null,\n    \"nextScreen\": \"KYC_INTRO\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\nnextScreen values:\n- HOME → verified, show home\n- KYC_INTRO → not started\n- KYC_UPLOAD → in progress\n- KYC_UNDER_REVIEW → all submitted, waiting for admin\n- KYC_RETRY → some docs rejected\n- ACCOUNT_SUSPENDED → driver suspended"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3. Me (verify token)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{driverToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/me",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "me"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth — Admin Login",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Signin (send OTP)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"9999999999\",\n  \"role\": \"admin\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/signin",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "signin"]
            },
            "description": "Admin phone is 9999999999 (seeded by migration 042). OTP in server console when SMS_PROVIDER=console."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Verify Signin (get token)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.success && json.data && json.data.tokens) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('adminToken', json.data.tokens.accessToken);",
                  "  console.log('Admin token saved');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"9999999999\",\n  \"otp\": \"{{adminOtp}}\",\n  \"role\": \"admin\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/verify-signin",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "verify-signin"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3. Me (verify token)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/me",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "me"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Driver — KYC",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET Status",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{driverToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/kyc/status",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "kyc", "status"]
            },
            "description": "Returns overall KYC status + per-doc status for all 6 types.\n\noverallStatus: not_started | in_progress | pending_review | verified | rejected | suspended\ncanGoOnline: true only when all 6 docs approved\ndocuments[]: { type, status, attemptsLeft, rejectionReason, canRetry }"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Submit — AADHAAR (front only)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{driverToken}}" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "document_type", "value": "AADHAAR", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "file",          "type": "file",      "src": "" }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/kyc/submit",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "kyc", "submit"]
            },
            "description": "Upload Aadhaar front. Max 5MB image / 1MB PDF.\n\nAlways returns status: manual_review (admin is final approver).\nextractedData: { name, dob, gender, state, masked }"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Submit — AADHAAR (front + back for address)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{driverToken}}" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "document_type", "value": "AADHAAR", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "file",          "type": "file",      "src": "", "description": "Aadhaar front" },
                { "key": "file_back",     "type": "file",      "src": "", "description": "Aadhaar back (optional — extracts address, pin_code)" }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/kyc/submit",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "kyc", "submit"]
            },
            "description": "Upload both sides of Aadhaar to also capture address and pin_code.\n\nfile_back is optional — if not provided, address fields will be null."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Submit — PAN",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{driverToken}}" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "document_type", "value": "PAN",  "type": "text" },
                { "key": "file",          "type": "file",  "src": "" }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/kyc/submit",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "kyc", "submit"]
            },
            "description": "Upload PAN card. Cashfree verifies against govt DB.\n\nextractedData: { name, father, dob, pan_status, aadhaar_linked, masked }\n\nHard block (cannot approve if): pan_status != 'E'"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Submit — DRIVING_LICENCE",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{driverToken}}" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "document_type", "value": "DRIVING_LICENCE", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "file",          "type": "file",              "src": "" }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/kyc/submit",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "kyc", "submit"]
            },
            "description": "Upload Driving Licence.\n\nextractedData: { name, guardian, dob, blood_group, address, issue_date, expiry_date, dl_status, photo_url, masked }\n\nSystem rejects if: expiry < 90 days\nHard block (cannot approve if): age < 18, dl_status != 'ACTIVE'"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Submit — VEHICLE_RC",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{driverToken}}" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "document_type", "value": "VEHICLE_RC", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "file",          "type": "file",         "src": "" }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/kyc/submit",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "kyc", "submit"]
            },
            "description": "Upload Vehicle RC.\n\nextractedData: { owner, relation_name, vehicle_model, vehicle_type, manufacturer, chassis_number, engine_number, registration_validity, masked }\n\nHard block (cannot approve if): registration_validity expired"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Submit — Bank Account",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{driverToken}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"account_number\": \"1234567890\",\n  \"ifsc\": \"HDFC0001234\",\n  \"name\": \"Rahul Sharma\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/kyc/bank",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "kyc", "bank"]
            },
            "description": "Penny-drop bank verification via Cashfree. Returns manual_review — admin approves.\n\nextractedData: { account_masked, ifsc, holder_name, bank_name, branch, city, account_status }"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Submit — Selfie (face match)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{driverToken}}" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "selfie", "type": "file", "src": "" }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/kyc/face-match",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "kyc", "face-match"]
            },
            "description": "Upload selfie. Aadhaar must already be submitted.\n\nCashfree matchFace runs against Aadhaar front:\n- similarity >= 75 → manual_review (high confidence)\n- similarity >= 60 → manual_review (medium confidence)\n- similarity < 60 → rejected (face mismatch)\n\nextractedData: { similarity_score, aadhaar_file_url } — admin sees both images for manual comparison."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Retry Document",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{driverToken}}" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "file", "type": "file", "src": "" }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/kyc/documents/{{docId}}/retry",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "kyc", "documents", "{{docId}}", "retry"]
            },
            "description": "Retry a system-rejected document. Max 3 attempts per doc type.\n\nSet docId to the documentId from the original submit response.\n\nFails if: attempt_count >= 3, or doc was admin-rejected with allowRetry=false."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Admin — Driver List",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET Drivers — All",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/kyc/admin/drivers?page=1&limit=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "kyc", "admin", "drivers"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "status", "value": "",   "description": "Filter: not_started | in_progress | pending_review | verified | rejected | suspended (optional)", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "page",   "value": "1" },
                { "key": "limit",  "value": "20" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Paginated list of all drivers with KYC summary.\n\nEach item: { user_id, full_name, phone_number, overall_status, submitted_docs_count, verified_docs_count, last_activity_at }\n\nUse ?status=pending_review to see drivers whose all docs are submitted and waiting for review."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET Drivers — Pending Review",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/kyc/admin/drivers?status=pending_review&page=1&limit=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "kyc", "admin", "drivers"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "status", "value": "pending_review" },
                { "key": "page",   "value": "1" },
                { "key": "limit",  "value": "20" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET Driver KYC Detail",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.success && json.data && json.data.documents) {",
                  "  var pending = json.data.documents.find(d => d.status === 'manual_review');",
                  "  if (pending) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('docId', pending.id);",
                  "    console.log('First pending doc ID saved:', pending.id, '| type:', pending.document_type);",
                  "  }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/kyc/admin/drivers/{{driverUserId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "kyc", "admin", "drivers", "{{driverUserId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Full KYC detail for one driver — all 6 documents in one call.\n\nResponse:\n```json\n{\n  \"driver\": {\n    \"id\": \"...\",\n    \"full_name\": \"Rahul Sharma\",\n    \"phone_number\": \"9876543210\",\n    \"overall_status\": \"pending_review\",\n    \"pre_check_report\": { \"passed\": [...], \"failed\": [...], \"warnings\": [...] }\n  },\n  \"documents\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": 1,\n      \"document_type\": \"AADHAAR\",\n      \"status\": \"manual_review\",\n      \"file_url\": \"https://...\",\n      \"extracted_data\": { \"name\": \"...\", \"dob\": \"...\", ... },\n      \"confidence_score\": 85,\n      \"attempt_count\": 1,\n      \"reviewed_by_name\": null\n    },\n    ...\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nTests script auto-saves first pending doc ID to {{docId}}."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Admin — Doc Actions",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET Doc Queue — Pending Review",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/kyc/admin/queue?status=manual_review&page=1&limit=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "kyc", "admin", "queue"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "status", "value": "manual_review", "description": "manual_review | rejected | all" },
                { "key": "type",   "value": "",              "description": "AADHAAR | PAN | DRIVING_LICENCE | VEHICLE_RC | BANK_ACCOUNT | SELFIE (optional)", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "page",   "value": "1" },
                { "key": "limit",  "value": "20" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Doc-level queue — all documents in manual_review state.\n\nUse ?status=rejected to see system-rejected docs admin can override.\nUse ?status=all for both.\nUse ?type=SELFIE to filter by doc type."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET Doc Queue — System Rejected (admin can override)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/kyc/admin/queue?status=rejected&page=1&limit=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "kyc", "admin", "queue"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "status", "value": "rejected" },
                { "key": "page",   "value": "1" },
                { "key": "limit",  "value": "20" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "System-auto-rejected docs. Admin can approve these if the rejection was a false positive.\n\nNote: Admin-rejected docs (reviewed_by is set) CANNOT be re-approved."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET Doc Detail",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/kyc/admin/documents/{{docId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "kyc", "admin", "documents", "{{docId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Single document detail. Includes extracted_data, file_url, driver info, fraud_score, attempt_count."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Approve Document",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"notes\": \"Document verified — clear and authentic\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/kyc/admin/documents/{{docId}}/approve",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "kyc", "admin", "documents", "{{docId}}", "approve"]
            },
            "description": "Approve a document (manual_review or system-rejected).\n\nTriggers aggregate recompute — if all 6 docs approved, driver overall_status becomes 'verified'.\nDriver gets push notification.\n\nHard blocks (returns 400):\n- Document already approved\n- Admin-rejected doc (reviewed_by is set)\n- Document tampering detected (is_overwritten / is_photo_imposed)\n- Duplicate document (registered with another driver)\n- Driver age < 18 (DL)\n- DL status != ACTIVE\n- PAN status != E (inactive)\n- RC registration expired"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Reject Document (with retry)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"reason\": \"Image is blurry — please upload a clearer photo\",\n  \"allowRetry\": true\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/kyc/admin/documents/{{docId}}/reject",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "kyc", "admin", "documents", "{{docId}}", "reject"]
            },
            "description": "Reject a document. reason is shown to the driver.\n\nallowRetry: true → driver can resubmit (up to 3 attempts total)\nallowRetry: false → sets attempt_count=3, driver must contact support\n\nOnce admin rejects, this decision is FINAL — cannot be re-approved."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Reject Document (no retry — final)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"reason\": \"Document appears fraudulent — tampered image detected\",\n  \"allowRetry\": false\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/kyc/admin/documents/{{docId}}/reject",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "kyc", "admin", "documents", "{{docId}}", "reject"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET Fraud Alerts",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/kyc/admin/fraud-alerts?severity=HIGH",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "kyc", "admin", "fraud-alerts"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "severity", "value": "HIGH", "description": "HIGH | MEDIUM | LOW (optional — omit for all)" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Fraud flags across all documents.\n\nFlag types: DUPLICATE_NUMBER | NAME_MISMATCH | VELOCITY | TEMPLATE_TAMPERING | FACE_MISMATCH | EXPIRED_DOC | CROSS_DOC_MISMATCH"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Suspend Driver",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"reason\": \"Repeated fraudulent document submissions\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/kyc/admin/drivers/{{driverUserId}}/suspend",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "kyc", "admin", "drivers", "{{driverUserId}}", "suspend"]
            },
            "description": "Manually suspend a driver. Sets overall_status = suspended.\nDriver cannot go online after suspension."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
